title: Missing items in match history
body:
Hi I just downloaded new patch and went to my match history.

In my past few games it shows an item missing (eg. I played Trundle and the boots are missing in the match history)
The problem is pretty much missing boots {{champion:6}} Anyone else got the issue too?

replies.body:
I just checked on my client and it seems that the last game I played, before the patch, is missing the boots in my match history. (If I view this game on the web - I do see them) I also see boots in all my other games within the client.

Anyone else seeing something like this?
